WEBVTT

1
00:01:30.980 --> 00:01:34.070
This story is a work of fiction. The names of all of the characters, organizations, and so on
 are imaginary. It also bears no connection to any specific real-life events.

2
00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:39.410
Episode 11: Reducing Two to One

3
00:01:44.520 --> 00:01:46.330
A letter from Concubine Gyokuyou?

4
00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:49.530
Yes. I was ordered to deliver it directly.

5
00:01:49.530 --> 00:01:52.650
Lady Ah-Duo is away on a tea party.

6
00:01:56.340 --> 00:01:59.680
There's something I would like to 
discuss with you, Lady Fengming.

7
00:02:00.500 --> 00:02:01.780
I understand.

8
00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:15.230
The luggage is all packed up. 
That must mean, as I thought...

9
00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:16.650
Please.

10
00:02:22.530 --> 00:02:25.820
So, what did you need today?

11
00:02:25.820 --> 00:02:28.170
We've finished cleaning this place.

12
00:02:28.170 --> 00:02:30.000
When are you moving out?

13
00:02:32.930 --> 00:02:34.710
You're a smart one.

14
00:02:35.070 --> 00:02:37.750
The big clean-up was an excuse.

15
00:02:38.220 --> 00:02:42.810
In order to welcome a new high-ranked 
concubine during the new year's celebration,

16
00:02:42.810 --> 00:02:46.060
Concubine Ah-Duo must leave this palace.

17
00:02:47.860 --> 00:02:50.770
Concubine Ah-Duo can't have
 children anymore, can she?

18
00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:55.610
What happened when she gave birth?

19
00:02:55.610 --> 00:02:58.940
I fail to see how that's any of your business.

20
00:02:59.990 --> 00:03:01.910
It is my business.

21
00:03:04.270 --> 00:03:07.790
The doctor who attended 
that birth was my father.

22
00:03:10.040 --> 00:03:12.700
My guess is the misfortune was 
that Concubine Ah-Duo,

23
00:03:12.700 --> 00:03:14.330
the prince's concubine at the time,

24
00:03:14.330 --> 00:03:18.050
gave birth at the same time 
as the empress dowager.

25
00:03:27.220 --> 00:03:29.310
When is the doctor coming back?!

26
00:03:29.310 --> 00:03:31.000
He's still at the empress dowager's.

27
00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:31.940
Lady Ah-Duo!

28
00:03:31.940 --> 00:03:35.690
Lady Ah-Duo, it's all right! 
Fengming is by your side!

29
00:03:35.690 --> 00:03:38.160
The empress dowager was given higher priority,

30
00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:40.950
and Concubine Ah-Duo's childbirth had to wait.

31
00:03:47.630 --> 00:03:48.830
Lady Ah-Duo.

32
00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:53.710
That must have been when 
Concubine Ah-Duo lost her uterus.

33
00:03:54.870 --> 00:04:00.090
The child that was born to Concubine 
Ah-Duo then passed away soon after.

34
00:04:01.380 --> 00:04:05.000
Lady Fengming, are you 
blaming yourself for that?

35
00:04:05.470 --> 00:04:12.560
You must have been the one taking care of 
the baby instead of Concubine Ah-Duo.

36
00:04:15.190 --> 00:04:17.430
You've figured it all out,

37
00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:21.570
despite being the daughter of the quack 
who couldn't help Lady Ah-Duo.

38
00:04:23.860 --> 00:04:25.280
You're right.

39
00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:26.280
...Luomen, expelled...

40
00:04:28.030 --> 00:04:30.640
It's thought that the cause 
of the baby's death was

41
00:04:30.640 --> 00:04:33.540
the same toxic make-up
 from the other incidents,

42
00:04:34.560 --> 00:04:36.130
but that's not the case, is it?

43
00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:42.840
That doctor you call a quack 
must have banned that powder.

44
00:04:43.150 --> 00:04:47.760
You're a wise person. You wouldn't
 have let the baby die from that.

45
00:04:47.760 --> 00:04:51.400
The real cause of death was this.

46
00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:56.160
Many flowers have poison in them,

47
00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:58.800
like aconite or azalea.

48
00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:01.110
Their nectar can be poisonous, too.

49
00:05:02.050 --> 00:05:03.610
I am aware.

50
00:05:03.610 --> 00:05:05.350
But back then...

51
00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:07.320
you weren't.

52
00:05:07.610 --> 00:05:10.330
You didn't realize regular 
honey with no poison,

53
00:05:10.800 --> 00:05:13.660
the medicine you thought was good for health,

54
00:05:14.680 --> 00:05:16.790
can be harmful to a newborn baby.

55
00:05:21.080 --> 00:05:23.560
Thank you for your help as always, Fengming.

56
00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:26.720
It's no trouble at all, Lady Ah-Duo.

57
00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:28.800
Please rest and recover soon.

58
00:05:33.270 --> 00:05:36.460
And thus, Concubine Ah-Duo's child passed away.

59
00:05:38.530 --> 00:05:40.810
The cause was treated as a mystery.

60
00:05:40.810 --> 00:05:43.800
My father Luomen, the attending 
doctor at the time,

61
00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:47.800
was blamed for the repeated mistakes, 
including the one at childbirth.

62
00:05:47.800 --> 00:05:49.740
He was expelled from the rear palace.

63
00:05:50.450 --> 00:05:55.830
But later on, you accidentally learned 
the true cause of the baby's death.

64
00:05:57.510 --> 00:06:02.040
Someone taught you that honey can be 
poisonous to infants, didn't they?

65
00:06:04.170 --> 00:06:07.180
You had to make sure 
Concubine Ah-Duo didn't find out.

66
00:06:07.180 --> 00:06:10.300
She couldn't know you were 
the one who killed her only child.

67
00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:14.310
So, you tried to eliminate them.

68
00:06:15.010 --> 00:06:16.560
That person is...

69
00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:20.140
Concubine Lishu.

70
00:06:22.280 --> 00:06:23.820
During the previous emperor's reign,

71
00:06:23.820 --> 00:06:27.900
Concubine Lishu was close to 
Concubine Ah-Duo, who was her elder.

72
00:06:28.320 --> 00:06:31.070
Concubine Ah-Duo was also 
fond of Concubine Lishu.

73
00:06:31.630 --> 00:06:34.330
A young girl, taken from her parents,

74
00:06:34.920 --> 00:06:37.780
and a woman who could no longer give birth.

75
00:06:38.960 --> 00:06:41.930
There may have been a type of 
codependency developing.

76
00:06:42.580 --> 00:06:44.990
During that time, you learned
 from Concubine Lishu

77
00:06:44.990 --> 00:06:48.090
that she almost died eating honey as a baby.

78
00:06:49.920 --> 00:06:52.520
To make sure Concubine Ah-Duo 
never heard that story,

79
00:06:52.520 --> 00:06:55.450
you started to chase Concubine Lishu 
away from the Garnet Pavilion.

80
00:06:56.480 --> 00:06:59.400
Later, the previous emperor passed away,

81
00:06:59.400 --> 00:07:03.650
and Concubine Lishu was forced to leave the
 rear palace, unaware of why she was chased out.

82
00:07:06.110 --> 00:07:09.230
You must have felt quite relieved.

83
00:07:09.230 --> 00:07:12.820
But Concubine Lishu, who you 
thought you'd never see again,

84
00:07:13.260 --> 00:07:15.080
returned to the rear palace.

85
00:07:16.330 --> 00:07:18.520
As another high-ranking concubine.

86
00:07:18.520 --> 00:07:21.060
As a threat to Concubine Ah-Duo's status.

87
00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:26.120
That insolent child tried to visit 
Concubine Ah-Duo many times,

88
00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:28.380
as if trying to be with her mother.

89
00:07:29.780 --> 00:07:32.830
To protect Concubine Ah-Duo, 
who is incapable of childbirth,

90
00:07:32.830 --> 00:07:35.850
and to hide the issue with the honey...

91
00:07:36.320 --> 00:07:39.890
You poisoned Concubine Lishu's soup.

92
00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:45.610
What do you want?

93
00:07:46.320 --> 00:07:47.940
There's nothing.

94
00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:51.980
Anything. Just ask.

95
00:07:59.110 --> 00:08:02.660
You must know that's meaningless.

96
00:08:21.980 --> 00:08:28.690
Hey. Do you know what's most precious 
to the person most precious to you?

97
00:08:31.070 --> 00:08:34.000
The moment I met Lady Ah-Duo,

98
00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:37.660
I knew I would never serve anyone else again.

99
00:08:38.210 --> 00:08:39.660
Despite being a woman,

100
00:08:39.660 --> 00:08:43.370
she had a strong will, and the ability 
to speak on even grounds with the prince.

101
00:08:44.280 --> 00:08:47.130
I had nothing but the deepest 
respect for Lady Ah-Duo.

102
00:08:47.580 --> 00:08:52.280
Compared to me, who just followed my 
parents' orders to become a lady-in-waiting,

103
00:08:52.280 --> 00:08:54.840
she was such an astonishing person.

104
00:08:56.290 --> 00:08:57.740
Despite that, I...

105
00:08:58.820 --> 00:09:03.110
I took what was most precious 
to her with my own hands...

106
00:09:03.680 --> 00:09:05.630
I took him away!

107
00:09:05.630 --> 00:09:09.020
The baby that Lady Ah-Duo loved so dearly!

108
00:09:10.230 --> 00:09:11.480
With these hands!

109
00:09:12.150 --> 00:09:13.270
Back then...

110
00:09:14.130 --> 00:09:16.450
Lady Ah-Duo told us this.

111
00:09:17.010 --> 00:09:19.350
Do not blame yourselves for this.

112
00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:22.660
Babies can die for any
 reason until they're seven.

113
00:09:23.060 --> 00:09:26.120
Even the slightest illness 
can easily kill them.

114
00:09:26.560 --> 00:09:30.310
My baby simply followed 
the will of the heavens.

115
00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:42.150
And yet, I knew she cried 
herself to sleep every night!

116
00:09:50.360 --> 00:09:54.940
What was her mental state like, as she served 
Lady Ah-Duo for the past sixteen years?

117
00:09:55.940 --> 00:10:00.700
Without having her own partner, 
sacrificing everything for Concubine Ah-Duo...

118
00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:03.040
I can't relate.

119
00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:07.960
I don't have it in my heart 
to keep someone so close.

120
00:10:09.370 --> 00:10:14.040
If he hears my story, Master Jinshi 
will surely apprehend Fengming.

121
00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:17.540
There's no way she'd 
escape capital punishment.

122
00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:21.820
She's a smart woman. She knows all of that.

123
00:10:24.340 --> 00:10:26.390
I have a suggestion.

124
00:10:30.100 --> 00:10:34.860
The only thing I can do is to take 
your two motives and make it one.

125
00:10:35.570 --> 00:10:37.180
It won't change the results.

126
00:10:37.840 --> 00:10:41.240
But if that's still preferable 
to you, please hear me out.

127
00:10:53.210 --> 00:10:54.570
So tired...

128
00:10:55.620 --> 00:10:58.810
A bath... No, it's too late for that.

129
00:10:58.810 --> 00:11:00.430
Guess I can at least get changed.

130
00:11:02.750 --> 00:11:06.380
I wore layers of stiffened 
oil paper, just in case.

131
00:11:06.380 --> 00:11:08.140
Glad I didn't need it.

132
00:11:08.560 --> 00:11:10.890
Getting slashed would hurt.

133
00:11:13.750 --> 00:11:17.900
And so, Fengming turned herself in.

134
00:11:17.900 --> 00:11:19.070
Do you know anything about it?

135
00:11:19.340 --> 00:11:20.950
What do you mean?

136
00:11:20.950 --> 00:11:24.060
I heard you had Gaoshun 
collect some information.

137
00:11:24.060 --> 00:11:28.620
Yes. I'd hoped to figure something 
out, but it was all for naught.

138
00:11:30.160 --> 00:11:34.480
Fengming's motive, as you said, 
was to try to make sure

139
00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:37.750
Concubine Ah-Duo could stay in the 
position of one of the four concubines.

140
00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:39.510
I see.

141
00:11:39.840 --> 00:11:44.300
But Concubine Ah-Duo has already been 
determined to leave the rear palace.

142
00:11:44.300 --> 00:11:48.010
She'll live in the detached 
palace to the south.

143
00:11:48.610 --> 00:11:51.280
Does this incident have 
anything to do with that?

144
00:11:51.280 --> 00:11:53.520
No, the decision was made a while ago.

145
00:11:54.240 --> 00:11:56.490
It was the emperor's call.

146
00:11:56.490 --> 00:11:57.520
I see.

147
00:11:59.250 --> 00:12:00.150
This flower.

148
00:12:01.120 --> 00:12:03.530
Hongniang came by earlier to put it on display.

149
00:12:05.380 --> 00:12:07.860
Yes, it's out of season.

150
00:12:17.520 --> 00:12:18.590
It's sweet.

151
00:12:18.590 --> 00:12:19.590
Poisonous, though.

152
00:12:21.490 --> 00:12:24.380
It's not lethal. Don't worry.

153
00:12:26.400 --> 00:12:29.060
My suggestion to Fengming, back then...

154
00:12:31.040 --> 00:12:34.780
The poisoning of Concubine Lishu. 
The cause of death for the baby.

155
00:12:34.780 --> 00:12:37.040
If these two motives become one,

156
00:12:37.040 --> 00:12:41.400
she could hide the cause of the baby's 
death from Concubine Ah-Duo.

157
00:12:42.340 --> 00:12:44.550
Even if her own death is inevitable...

158
00:12:45.340 --> 00:12:50.490
That was the best I could do, 
as a girl with no power.

159
00:13:04.210 --> 00:13:05.550
I can't sleep.

160
00:13:07.510 --> 00:13:09.510
Maybe I'll take a walk.

161
00:13:30.820 --> 00:13:33.050
Fengming was executed.

162
00:13:33.610 --> 00:13:36.790
Concubine Ah-Duo is set to leave 
the rear palace tomorrow.

163
00:13:37.620 --> 00:13:39.580
Oh, someone beat me here?

164
00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:46.340
You're that girl who came 
to help clean the other day.

165
00:13:46.340 --> 00:13:48.240
I'll leave right away.

166
00:13:48.240 --> 00:13:49.180
No.

167
00:13:49.740 --> 00:13:51.510
Care to join me for a drink?

168
00:13:52.260 --> 00:13:54.220
Whoa! Booze!

169
00:13:55.520 --> 00:13:57.160
Thank you very much.

170
00:14:06.850 --> 00:14:08.440
Pretty masculine, aren't I?

171
00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:11.820
I feel like you're giving
 that impression on purpose.

172
00:14:13.430 --> 00:14:15.250
You're an honest one.

173
00:14:16.680 --> 00:14:24.150
After my son left me, I became 
the emperor's friend, not his concubine.

174
00:14:24.690 --> 00:14:28.340
Or rather, I returned to being his friend.

175
00:14:29.910 --> 00:14:33.060
I never thought I'd become a concubine.

176
00:14:34.500 --> 00:14:37.780
I was a concubine in name only, 
given the role out of pity.

177
00:14:38.360 --> 00:14:41.110
I wanted to hand it off to someone 
else as soon as possible.

178
00:14:42.640 --> 00:14:45.360
Why cling to it for so long...?

179
00:14:45.970 --> 00:14:51.350
She probably would have said the same 
things to whoever she'd met up here.

180
00:14:56.850 --> 00:14:59.420
It must have been cold in that water.

181
00:15:00.920 --> 00:15:03.000
It must have been painful.

182
00:15:07.700 --> 00:15:08.920
You're probably right.

183
00:15:09.920 --> 00:15:11.510
Stupid, don't you think?

184
00:15:13.240 --> 00:15:14.870
Perhaps she was.

185
00:15:16.600 --> 00:15:18.330
We're all stupid.

186
00:15:25.400 --> 00:15:27.160
Perhaps we are.

187
00:15:36.550 --> 00:15:38.390
I think I get it now.

188
00:15:40.040 --> 00:15:43.430
That servant was indeed a suicide.

189
00:15:44.090 --> 00:15:46.490
Concubine Ah-Duo noticed that.

190
00:15:47.130 --> 00:15:50.580
Maybe Fengming helped set it up.

191
00:15:51.700 --> 00:15:54.360
To take suspicion away from Concubine Ah-Duo,

192
00:15:54.360 --> 00:15:56.940
the servant chose to sink down 
into the cold water.

193
00:15:57.600 --> 00:15:59.950
To keep her secret hidden,

194
00:15:59.950 --> 00:16:02.650
Fengming chose to step up to the gallows.

195
00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:06.720
Regardless of Concubine
 Ah-Duo's own wishes,

196
00:16:06.720 --> 00:16:09.880
there are those who 
sacrifice their lives for her.

197
00:16:11.830 --> 00:16:14.200
I should go now, too.

198
00:16:17.880 --> 00:16:19.200
What are you doing?

199
00:16:23.090 --> 00:16:25.320
Ow... Who's that? You startled me.

200
00:16:25.320 --> 00:16:27.020
My bad.

201
00:16:28.920 --> 00:16:30.880
Master Jinshi? Why are you here?

202
00:16:31.200 --> 00:16:33.340
I should ask the same of you.

203
00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:36.340
I'm sorry. I'll get up now—

204
00:16:37.750 --> 00:16:39.770
Could you let go?

205
00:16:40.430 --> 00:16:42.070
Let go, please.

206
00:16:43.480 --> 00:16:44.850
Don't wanna. It's too cold.

207
00:16:45.510 --> 00:16:49.400
You'll catch a cold without a coat. 
Please go back to your room.

208
00:16:50.070 --> 00:16:52.020
Are you drunk?

209
00:16:52.420 --> 00:16:54.610
I had to. I was sharing a drink with someone.

210
00:16:54.910 --> 00:16:56.630
Sharing, huh?

211
00:16:57.130 --> 00:16:59.640
The host invited me to drink,

212
00:16:59.640 --> 00:17:01.440
loaded me up full of booze,

213
00:17:01.440 --> 00:17:03.530
then just took off.

214
00:17:04.200 --> 00:17:06.420
When she finally came back,

215
00:17:06.720 --> 00:17:09.720
she told me she was satisfied
 now, and threw me out.

216
00:17:10.490 --> 00:17:15.880
I didn't know anyone in this rear 
palace could treat this guy like that.

217
00:17:15.880 --> 00:17:19.040
But that's not related to this right now.

218
00:17:19.040 --> 00:17:22.310
I don't want to put up with a clingy drunk.

219
00:17:22.710 --> 00:17:28.620
Wait... Come to think of it, 
he did catch me as I fell.

220
00:17:28.620 --> 00:17:33.030
Maybe it's rude to just make him let go 
of me without even thanking him.

221
00:17:33.570 --> 00:17:34.870
Master Jinshi—

222
00:17:45.110 --> 00:17:46.790
Just a little longer.

223
00:17:47.510 --> 00:17:50.700
Keep me warm, just a little longer.

224
00:18:07.590 --> 00:18:11.060
Neither of them seem hungover.

225
00:18:11.360 --> 00:18:13.480
Concubine Ah-Duo, in order
 to leave the rear palace,

226
00:18:13.480 --> 00:18:15.610
returns the crown signifying 
her as Pure Concubine.

227
00:18:16.470 --> 00:18:22.120
That crown will be bestowed on another girl 
who will join the rear palace later.

228
00:18:28.410 --> 00:18:30.360
Ah, I see.

229
00:18:30.360 --> 00:18:32.460
I knew she resembled someone.

230
00:18:33.120 --> 00:18:35.460
It's Master Jinshi.

231
00:18:36.840 --> 00:18:40.470
Those two might as well swap outfits...

232
00:18:41.160 --> 00:18:42.470
Swap...

233
00:18:43.320 --> 00:18:46.560
After my son left me...

234
00:18:46.560 --> 00:18:50.560
"Left me," she said. Not "died"?

235
00:18:51.170 --> 00:18:54.510
I can almost interpret that 
to mean he's still alive.

236
00:18:54.510 --> 00:18:59.210
Concubine Ah-Duo's child and 
the then-empress dowager's child...

237
00:18:59.210 --> 00:19:02.230
What if the two babies were swapped?

238
00:19:03.200 --> 00:19:07.250
It must have been clear to Concubine Ah-Duo, 
through her experience in childbirth.

239
00:19:07.530 --> 00:19:10.040
What are you doing?! I must 
tend to Concubine Ah-Duo...

240
00:19:10.040 --> 00:19:11.740
The empress dowager takes priority!

241
00:19:11.740 --> 00:19:13.610
N-No!

242
00:19:13.610 --> 00:19:18.600
After all, she was just a nurse's daughter, 
a childhood friend of the prince.

243
00:19:18.600 --> 00:19:23.800
Her son would live a better life 
as the empress dowager's son.

244
00:19:24.930 --> 00:19:29.270
Maybe she wasn't in a state 
to decide what was right or wrong.

245
00:19:29.760 --> 00:19:33.190
But if the decision resulted
 in her son surviving...

246
00:19:33.940 --> 00:19:37.020
That would have been all that 
Concubine Ah-Duo could have wished for.

247
00:19:37.720 --> 00:19:41.220
What if people found out 
the babies were swapped later?

248
00:19:41.760 --> 00:19:44.440
If that was after the one baby had died,

249
00:19:44.440 --> 00:19:50.120
that would explain why my dad would be 
physically punished for not noticing.

250
00:19:51.590 --> 00:19:53.120
And if that were the case,

251
00:19:53.120 --> 00:19:56.540
it would explain why the emperor's younger 
brother is in a delicate position,

252
00:19:57.260 --> 00:20:00.240
and why Concubine Ah-Duo, 
who's supposed to be a realist,

253
00:20:00.240 --> 00:20:02.900
stayed in the rear palace for so long...

254
00:20:06.100 --> 00:20:09.630
Complete nonsense. 
An idiotic delusion of a story.

255
00:20:09.630 --> 00:20:10.850
Please, wait!

256
00:20:10.850 --> 00:20:12.190
Lady Lishu!

257
00:20:15.880 --> 00:20:17.730
As always.

258
00:20:18.960 --> 00:20:23.130
As a lonely concubine, to have 
a lady-in-waiting she can trust...

259
00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:27.240
How reassuring that must be.

260
00:20:29.240 --> 00:20:30.250
Lady Lishu!

261
00:20:38.230 --> 00:20:44.860
At that moment, her masculine, noble face
 suddenly took on the expression of a mother.

262
00:20:52.990 --> 00:20:56.010
Here is the list of Fengming's family 
and those connected to them.

263
00:20:57.350 --> 00:21:00.820
I heard she was kidnapped and sold off, but...

264
00:21:06.120 --> 00:21:09.940
Not just some superficial sweetness

265
00:21:12.330 --> 00:21:17.260
I want more warmth than I can even use, oh

266
00:21:18.540 --> 00:21:23.590
Having these selfish idealistic thoughts

267
00:21:23.590 --> 00:21:28.160
I swallowed them again today 
before putting them into words

268
00:21:28.730 --> 00:21:33.330
Still in my memories, 
the scent of fragrant olive

269
00:21:33.330 --> 00:21:36.450
The color of twilight in the city

270
00:21:36.450 --> 00:21:41.270
We were laughing...

271
00:21:41.270 --> 00:21:53.180
Filled with sadness, 
the tears welled up in my eyes

272
00:21:53.710 --> 00:22:01.400
I found a glow during those days

273
00:22:01.400 --> 00:22:05.460
I guess I took everything for granted

274
00:22:06.080 --> 00:22:18.500
The wind was so loud I covered my ears

275
00:22:18.500 --> 00:22:26.040
I gotta stop being like that

276
00:22:26.040 --> 00:22:34.240
Even if I stumble over the words of love

277
00:22:35.040 --> 00:22:50.050
Next Time

278
00:22:46.480 --> 00:22:49.540
Next time: "The Eunuch 
and the Courtesan."

279
00:22:46.590 --> 00:22:50.050
Episode 12: The Eunuch and the Courtesan
